  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Despite multiple credibility factors with achieved levels below required levels, this package incorrectly declares assuranceLevel High and an Accepted decision outcome, triggering COMPOUND-03 (assurance-level overstatement). Full 13-factor assessment is included; several factors show critical gaps between required and achieved levels.",
